HEADWORD: Rememberable
<hw>Re*mem"ber*a*ble</hw> <pr>(-?-b'l)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable
or worthy of being remembered.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Re*mem"ber*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms> <-- =
memorable -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The whole vale of Keswick is so <qex>rememberable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

